commits.message:
1. Switched JSON scanner to produce decimals instead of doubles.
2. Switched keyword lookup to use HashSet vs Enum.Parse, which sould be more efficient and does not throw ArgumentExceptions.
3. Updated unit tests.
Updated reference assembly
Fix broken config setting parsing.
Make index cache size configurable. Misc. bug fixes and added new tests.
Updated to latest build of RazorDB which includes enhancements for shared cache. Added shared RazorCache on ObjectStores and made cache size configurable.

FIX - Made first ID returned from ObjectIDStore always be 1 no matter if the ID store already exists or not (previous behavior was to return 0 if access the ObjectIDStore for the first time and 1 if the ObjectIDStore had been truncated).
UPDATED TEST - Updated BulkStore test to include a DateTime index value.
Updated a few notes in the README
Added missing SQLite driver implementation for Count operation.
Added caching to Indexer Count functions. Also made indexer cache more generic in that it does not only store ObjectIDs anymore, but count values as well.
Expanded Object Count by Index capability and exposed functionality via client interface.
Fixed bug when bulk storing into Object Stores that do not have any indexes. Also, added a method to the ObjectService to report the current Object ID for a given object store.
Exposed BulkStore capability through Object Service Client interface.

Added configurable Object Store auto-close. When enabled, Object Stores will be closed after they are idle for a specified timeout period. This will free up file handles and memory being utilized by infrequently used Object Stores.
Cleanup in README
Integrate new cache cleaner into Object Service. Additional unit testing.
Additional multi-threaded unit testing on the Indexer Cache.
Minor unit test change
Finished work on HardPrune cache cleaner. New tests and fixes to Indexer cache.
Additional Indexer cache testing and fixes.
Dispose lock in Version Store.
Continue work on indexer cache - bug fixes and unit tests.
Some re-working of the ObjectIndexerCache to improve threading, fix bugs, and improve the structure of the code for use with cache cleaners (work in progress). Updated and added unit tests.
Added new unit test for generating many index queries over a range of unique index values.
Added appdir placeholder capability to Config object's ObjectServiceDataDir property. Updated unit tests for Config object.
Added capability to tap into the ObjectVersionChanged event and basic unit test.
Added missing thread lock to ObjectIDStore. Added new tests to validate functionality of the ObjectIDStore. Updated concurrency handling of ObjectVersionStore to use ReaderWriterLock.
Added caching to Object Metadata Store. New metadata tests to improve test coverage.
Updated Object Service Client interface for new RemoveBySecondaryKey function.
Added RemoveBySecondaryKey function and unit tests.
Updated README
Removing JS files - project will focus solely on .NET code.
Fixed confusing property naming on cache entries.
Added UpdateIndex function. Initial work begun on query cache cleanup capability.
Update to latest release of RazorDB V1

Added a demo project that demonstrates how the ZeroG ObjectService can be used in a web service. The demo site uses Web API and allows "activity" objects to be added, updated, and deleted. It demonstrates a basic object usage pattern including indexing.
Updated Readme
Add index exists check to SQLite Indexer CreateIndex SQL.
Enhanced SQLite connection string handling to support {AppDir} placeholder setting.
Added new test. Updated reference library.
Bug fixes and unit testing. Expanded functions available on ObjectServiceClient.
Improved connection handling
Updated readme
Added some comments
Updated test
Wired up indexer Count methods to the ObjectService. Added more BulkStore test with lots of records
Added SQLite DatabaseService driver. A few minor fixes in Indexer and MySQL/SQLServer implementations.
Added null index and BulkStore capability.
Additional unit testing
Markdown based README and LICENSE file.
Finish SQL bulk insert implementation. Integrate bulk insert into object indexer and restore operation. Added extended configuration property support to Database Service.
Work started on BulkInsert support
Added Count and Iterate to ObjectService
Expand client interface capability. Fix bug in JSON to SQL generator. Some refactoring in ObjectService and new tests.
Work on client API and related refactorings
Implement ObjectService.Restore and tests
Continued work on BackupReader/Writer and tests.
Preliminary work on BackupReader started.
Remove obsolete file
Fix binary index handling. Added ObjectStoreRecord and ObjectIndexRecord for serializing Object and Index iterator values. Finish ObjectBackupWriter and related tests.
Added missing file - was accidentally filtered by gitignore
Begin work on backup/restore.
Continue work on Iterator. More unit tests added.
Work on iterator
Finished Order support. Fixed bugs in SQL Server indexer. Started work on Iterate function.
Start work on Order By functionality in Indexer Find calls.
Make Find distinct
Refactor parameter passing to IndexProvider. Added limit support and tests.
Update test to support new index name restrictions. Added null test.
Bug fixing and refactoring tests to remove driver specific references. Config file can now be used to switch between drivers.
Update ObjectIndex implementation to simplify serialization model. New tests.
Added Count implementation and test
Added <= and >= sql constraint support. Started work on Exists and Count indexer functions.
Added client assembly and tests. Refactored shared classes.
Storage of larger values test
Fix bug in indexer caching. Added tests for secondary keys and caching.
Changed implementation of SecondaryKey to be its own K/V store.
Begin work on cache testing
Added max object dependencies config
Fix failing test
Update to support retrieving multiple values against a secondary key. Updated RazorDB reference to latest version, which prevents journal files from growing large.
Allow Config to be setup programatically and non-statically as well.
Refactoring nameSpace and object parameters. Removed ObjectCache (will focus on indexer cache first). Added object dependency validator and unit tests.

Initial work on Object Indexer cache. Cleanup of how namespace and object names are passed around internally. Added object dependencies. Changed object UniqueID to SecondaryKey and SecondaryKey is no longer automatically generated.
Initial work on caching
Removed direct reference to serializer class being used.
Added indexer Exists capability. Added new Find convenience functions. Added schema usage to SQL index provider.
Update ObjectID logic and more testing
Added ObjectService tests
Make indexer connections more configurable. More tests and fixes.
Added new Object Name Space management functions and unit tests. Fixed naming validations.
Fix like operator in both Index Provider's Find and in JSON to SQL generator.
Added tests to cover JSON tokenizer. Updated IndexProvider "simple" Find to allow Or and Like lookups. Added SQL Server setup scripts.
Bug fixing and unit testing
Integrate JSON to SQL generator into Index Providers. Additional unit testing.

Added type mapping capability to constraint generator.
Added more tests and bug fixes.
More unit testing and bug fixes
Refactoring and continued work on unit testing
Begin work on MySQL index provider and unit tests

1. Added mysql dll to References
2. Refactoring and cleanup in database service classes.
3. Added command text escaping when generating parameter name references
4. Refactoring and cleanup in JSON to SQL constraint generator.

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/jburman/ZeroG.git

Key/Value storage with indexing. Prototype index provider based on SQL Server (MySQL version coming next). First draft of JSON to SQL constraint generator for more flexible index query capability.
Begin Async support work.  Added GetDecimal to DatabaseHelper class.
Standard header
Added focusEl function.
Binary data support and additional DB specific naming helpers.
Removed MySQL dll from source control
Initial version of BSON tokenizer/walker/selector
Initial commit on BSONTokenizer
Begin work on JSONPath selector
Clarification of authorship in JS files.
Initial commit of JS helpers.
Updated README
Driver for using MySQL with ZeroG DatabaseService.
Driver for using SQL Server with ZeroG DatabaseService.
Initial commit on Data access library
Make exceptions thrown from JSONTokenizer more consistent.
Correct a spelling error.
Made exceptions thrown by the tokenizer more consistent (should all be JSONExceptions)
Added comments to clarify the behavior of certain events.
Removed "AllowMultiValue" selector option and added "IgnoreArrays" to clarify the intended behavior.
Removal of obsolete files from source control.
